In Hibernate Search 5, it was possible to define the index mapping path explicitly (`@IndexedEmbedded(prefix = ...)`) and use dots in the path which solved this issue, but Hibernate Search 6 doesn&#39;t support explicit dots in the path. 

Hopefully this example helps to illustrate. This is pseudo-ish code in transition from HS5 to HS6.
